{"title":"爷爷","authors":["刘勇"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":9,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘勇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我刚刚懂得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上边是天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下面是地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就衔着欢乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张开双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步三摇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扑进你大山般的心窝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的额头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我看见了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草地的颜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的双眼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我懂得了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝塔山的巍峨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的膝盖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我明白了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大渡河的铁索"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我记住了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗的脉搏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的身躯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给了我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老黄牛的品格"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那多雨的黄昏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用双肩扛着我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看不会后退的黄河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那太阳站起来的早晨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你领着我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读大中国的长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！爷爷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你永远地睡了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像干枯的河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请允许我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧上这红色的诗行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我的血液与你的血液"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在诗里融合"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}